'''''Jen'jidai''''' was the [[Sith (language)|Sith]] phrase for [[Dark Jedi/Legends|Dark Jedi]]. It specifically referred to the [[Exiles|Dark Jedi exiled]] from the [[Jedi Order/Legends|Jedi Order]] following the [[Battle of Corbos]] and arriving in [[Sith Worlds/Legends|Sith Space]].

